      <h2>Travel Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Bring warm clothing if trekking in the mountains.</li>
        <li>Respect local customs and traditions.</li>
        <li>Stay hydrated and carry snacks when trekking.</li>
        <li>Take a guide if you want to explore rural areas.</li>
